Just heard this song....The music is good but can't digest those lyrics. Personally I'm a big fan of Pritom...But I'm finding this kinda lyrics quite offensive as like as "Montu -tuni" character from "hazar bochor dhore" too.
Both the case are same. Story telling is excellent but not the story.... Here the musicians are excellent but not the lyrics.
Hard to digest
